<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password - Wonderful Books</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
    
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6600 0%, #ff8533 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;">
        <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700;">
            üîê Password Reset
        </h1>
        <p style="color: white; margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.9;">
            Reset your password to regain access to your account
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        
        <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #333;">
            Hello <strong><%= firstName %> <%= lastName %></strong>,
        </p>
        
        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #666; line-height: 1.7;">
            We received a request to reset the password for your <strong>Wonderful Books</strong> account. 
            If you made this request, click the button below to reset your password.
        </p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 35px 0;">
            <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" 
               style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6600 0%, #ff8533 100%); 
                      color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 25px; 
                      font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.3);
                      transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                üîì Reset My Password
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 25px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #856404; font-size: 14px;">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice:</strong> This password reset link will expire in 1 hour for your security. 
                If you don't use it within this time, you'll need to request a new one.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-top: 25px;">
            If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #007bff; word-break: break-all; background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #e9ecef;">
            <%= resetUrl %>
        </p>
        
        <hr style="border: none; height: 1px; background-color: #e9ecef; margin: 30px 0;">
        
        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
                <strong>üõ°Ô∏è Didn't request this password reset?</strong>
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
                No worries! Your account is still secure. You can safely ignore this email. 
                Your password won't be changed unless you click the reset link above.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin: 5px 0;">
                Happy Reading! üìö
            </p>
            <p style="color: #ff6600; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; margin: 5px 0;">
                The Wonderful Books Team
            </p>
        </div>
        
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px;">
        <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin: 5px 0;">
            This email was sent to <%= email %> because you requested a password reset.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin: 5px 0;">
            <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>" style="color: #999; text-decoration: underline;">Unsubscribe</a> | 
            <a href="mailto:<%= fromEmail %>" style="color: #999; text-decoration: underline;">Contact Support</a>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin: 15px 0 5px 0;">
            ¬© 2025 Wonderful Books. All rights reserved.
        </p>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>